_sText:
UPDATED: This is the FINAL of the remake of de_cpl_fire for CS:Source. 

Please feel free to host the map for download or on your gameserver, but make sure to update the map, as soon as the FINAL will be released!
Attention Server-Admins: Since the map is 26 MB with all the custom content, use net_maxfilesize 30 to allow download of the map.

Thanks to Casey from CAL for giving us the opportunity to make this remake and to Nightmare85 for rendering the cubemaps!

StarD00d & Magikus
www.d00ds.com
